# 2026-06-29-15-00 CST -- ETH -- LOSS -$62  (win 56%, n=9, fire 75%)

_CST hour 2026-06-29-15-00 = UTC 07:00-07:59 (settlements), entries 06:57-07:52 UTC._
_PnL figures are the PAPER signal at ~$1000/market notional. Real money was only ~$1/trade probes (LIVE fills below confirm the signal)._

## What happened
ETH traded 9 rounds (5-min up/down favorites), settling 5 wins / 4 losses = 55.6% win.
Strategy-pnl sum = **-$61.82** (matches the -$62 outlier). The loss is **BROAD, not concentrated**:
4 separate losing rounds, each ~-$23, against 5 wins of only ~+$4-7.

